really two towns.</i>

1113
01:19:15,376 --> 01:19:17,378
<i>Two sheriffs. Two mayors.</i>

1114
01:19:17,461 --> 01:19:19,589
<i>And in the end, two Phantoms.</i>

1115
01:19:21,131 --> 01:19:23,384
<i>After I came out of the
Redwater Bayous that night,</i>

1116
01:19:23,467 --> 01:19:26,061
