took Deputy Foster,</i>

1119
01:19:34,770 --> 01:19:38,070
<i>that the swamp gave him
the only burial he deserved.</i>

1120
01:19:38,148 --> 01:19:39,741
<i>Others believed I hadn't
killed the Phantom</i>

1121
01:19:39,817 --> 01:19:42,036
<i>'cause he was something
that couldn't be killed.</i>

1122
01:19:42,111 --> 01:19:44,205
